WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.760
I'm Emma Santer and I am the development manager here at Kitchens for Good. For the past five years,

00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:11.760
my job has been sharing the amazing work that our team is doing with our apprentices here in San

00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:18.240
Diego and I get to share that with individuals and companies and just our overall community to

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:23.440
